# Leitner Flashcards

Leitner Flashcards is a memorization tool that uses the Leitner system. It comes with 3-4 dummy questions and ~40
generic questions about Python.

In short, every question you answer correctly

Read more about the [Leitner system](https://www.mindedge.com/learning-science/the-leitner-system-how-does-it-work/)

## Installation

Fork the project

## Usage

python3 main.py

